-- ‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź‚ēź
function Nexus:LoadingScreen(opts)
    opts = opts or {}
    local title = opts.Title or "NexusUI"
    local sub = opts.Subtitle or "Loading..."
    local tasks = opts.Tasks or {}
    local T = (type(opts.Theme)=="table") and opts.Theme or Nexus.Themes[opts.Theme] or Nexus.Themes.BlackModern

    local sg = mkGui(99999)
    local bg = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(1,0,1,0), BackgroundColor3=T.bg, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=1, Parent=sg})

    -- Animated gradient overlay
    local gradient = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(1,0,1,0), BackgroundColor3=T.accent, BackgroundTransparency=0.97, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=2, Parent=bg})

    local vp = getVP()
    local CW = math.min(420, vp.X-60)
    local CH = 260 + #tasks*28
    
    -- Main card with glass effect
    local card = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,CW,0,CH), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(.5,.5),
        Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,.54,0), BackgroundColor3=T.glassBg,
        BackgroundTransparency=0.12, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=3, Parent=bg})
    N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(0,16), Parent=card})
    N("UIStroke",{Color=T.border, Thickness=1, Transparency=.35, Parent=card})

    -- Top glow stripe
    local topStripe = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,0,0,3), BackgroundColor3=T.accent, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
    N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(0,2), Parent=topStripe})

    -- Shimmer animation on stripe
    local shimmer = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,80,1,0), Position=UDim2.new(-0.3,0,0,0),
        BackgroundColor3=T.accentH, BackgroundTransparency=.4, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=topStripe})
    N("UIGradient",{Transparency=NumberSequence.new({
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0,1), NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0.4,0.3),
        NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(0.6,0.3), NumberSequenceKeypoint.new(1,1),
    }), Rotation=0, Parent=shimmer})

    tw(card,.45,{BackgroundTransparency=0.12, Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,.5,0)}, nil,nil,nil,function()
        twB(card, 0.25, {Size = UDim2.new(0,CW*1.01,0,CH*1.01)})
        task.wait(0.12)
        tw(card, 0.18, {Size = UDim2.new(0,CW,0,CH)})
    end)

    local y = 28
    N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,26), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=title, TextColor3=T.text, TextSize=22,
        Font=Enum.Font.GothamBold, ZIndex=4, Parent=card}); y=y+34
    local subLbl = N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,15), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=sub, TextColor3=T.sub, TextSize=12,
        Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, ZIndex=4, Parent=card}); y=y+24

    -- Task list
    local checks = {}
    for i,tk in ipairs(tasks) do
        local row = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,24), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
            BackgroundTransparency=1, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
        local dot = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,6,0,6), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(0,.5),
            Position=UDim2.new(0,0,.5,0), BackgroundColor3=T.muted, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=row})
        N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=dot})
        local tl = N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-14,1,0), Position=UDim2.new(0,14,0,0),
            BackgroundTransparency=1, Text=tk.Name or ("Task "..i), TextColor3=T.muted,
            TextSize=11, Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, TextXAlignment=Enum.TextXAlignment.Left, ZIndex=5, Parent=row})
        checks[i]={dot=dot,lbl=tl}; y=y+26
    end; y=y+10

    -- Progress bar
    local track = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,4), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundColor3=T.border, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
    N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=track})
    local barFill = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,0,1,0), BackgroundColor3=T.accent, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=track})
    N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=barFill}); y=y+12

    local pctL = N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(.5,0,0,15), Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text="0%", TextColor3=T.accent, TextSize=11,
        Font=Enum.Font.GothamBold, TextXAlignment=Enum.TextXAlignment.Right, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
    local curL = N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(.5,0,0,15), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,0,y),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text="", TextColor3=T.sub, TextSize=11,
        Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, TextXAlignment=Enum.TextXAlignment.Left, ZIndex=4, Parent=card}); y=y+20

    -- Animated dots
    local dF = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,60,0,12), AnchorPoint=Vector2.new(.5,0),
        Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,0,y), BackgroundTransparency=1, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})
    local ldots = {}
    for i=1,4 do
        local d = N("Frame",{Size=UDim2.new(0,7,0,7), Position=UDim2.new(0,(i-1)*15,0,1),
            BackgroundColor3=T.accent, BackgroundTransparency=.7, BorderSizePixel=0, ZIndex=5, Parent=dF})
        N("UICorner",{CornerRadius=UDim.new(1,0), Parent=d}); ldots[i]=d
    end
    N("TextLabel",{Size=UDim2.new(1,-32,0,13), Position=UDim2.new(0,16,1,-18),
        BackgroundTransparency=1, Text="NexusUI v7.0-Ultra", TextColor3=T.muted, TextSize=10,
        Font=Enum.Font.Gotham, ZIndex=4, Parent=card})

    -- Animate dots + shimmer
    local phase = 0
    local sc2 = RunService.Heartbeat:Connect(function(dt)
        phase = phase+dt*3
        for i,d in ipairs(ldots) do
            local t2=(math.sin(phase+(i-1)*1.57)+1)*.5
            d.BackgroundTransparency=lerp(.05,.85,1-t2)
            local s=lerp(4,9,t2); d.Size=UDim2.new(0,s,0,s)
        end
        local sp = ((phase*0.18) % 1.3) - 0.3
        shimmer.Position = UDim2.new(sp,0,0,0)
    end)

    local Loader={}
    local function setP(f2,lbl)
        tw(barFill,.28,{Size=UDim2.new(clamp(f2,0,1),0,1,0)})
        tw(topStripe,.28,{Size=UDim2.new(clamp(f2,0,1),0,0,3)})
        pctL.Text=math.floor(clamp(f2,0,1)*100).."%"
        if lbl then curL.Text=lbl end
    end

    function Loader:Run(cb)
        task.wait(.38)
        if #tasks==0 then
            for i=0,10 do setP(i/10,"Loading..."); task.wait(.07) end
        else
            for i,tk in ipairs(tasks) do
                setP((i-1)/#tasks, tk.Name or "...")
                if checks[i] then 
                    tw(checks[i].dot,.18,{BackgroundColor3=T.accent}) 
                    tw(checks[i].lbl,.18,{TextColor3=T.text}) 
                end
                task.wait(tk.Duration or .55)
                setP(i/#tasks)
                if checks[i] then
                    checks[i].dot.BackgroundColor3=T.success
                    checks[i].lbl.Text="‚úď "..(tk.Name or "")
                    checks[i].lbl.TextColor3=T.sub
                end
            end
        end
        setP(1,"Ready!"); curL.TextColor3=T.success
        task.wait(.45); sc2:Disconnect()
        twE(card,.35,{Size=UDim2.new(0,CW*0.92,0,CH*0.92),BackgroundTransparency=0.6})
        task.wait(.2)
        twI(card,.38,{BackgroundTransparency=1, Position=UDim2.new(.5,0,.45,0)})
        twI(bg,.45,{BackgroundTransparency=1}); task.wait(.48)
        pcall(function()sg:Destroy()end)
        if cb then task.spawn(cb) end
    end
    function Loader:SetStatus(t) subLbl.Text=t end
    function Loader:SetTask(t) curL.Text=t end
    function Loader:SetProgress(f2) setP(f2) end
    return Loader
end

